# 🏋️ Gym Trainer Website – SoftGrowTech Task

## 📌 Project Overview
This project is developed as part of the SoftGrowTech Task.  
It is a modern and responsive Gym Trainer website designed to showcase fitness services, membership plans, and facilities.

The website provides a clean user interface and a smooth experience for users to explore gym services and contact trainers easily.

## 🚀 Features
- Responsive Design (Mobile + Desktop)
- Modern UI/UX
- Navigation Menu
- Banner Slider
- About Section
- Services Section
- Membership Plans
- Facilities Section
- Contact Form
- Social Media Links

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Bootstrap
- JavaScript
- jQuery
- Font Awesome

## 📁 Folder Structure
